<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1134,288,757]" box="[151,741,288,315]" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">
<heading box="[151,741,288,315]" fontSize="11" level="2" pageId="2" pageNumber="125" reason="2">
<taxonomicName authority="(Stys &amp; Moucha, 1962)" baseAuthorityName="Stys &amp; Moucha" baseAuthorityYear="1962" box="[151,741,288,315]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Dasysyrphus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="125" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="postclaviger">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,741,288,315]" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,456,288,315]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">Dasysyrphus postclaviger</emphasis>
(Stys &amp; Moucha, 1962)
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1134,288,757]" box="[151,362,322,348]" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">Matériel examiné:</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="125" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1134,288,757]" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">• 1 exemplaire de la collection ETH, révisé par L. Fisler. Provenance: Vercorin (VS), collecté en 1891 par E. Favre.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1134,288,757]" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">
• 10 exemplaires de la collection BNM, révisés par L. Fisler. Provenances: Antönien (GR), Berg-Cania-Aldur (GR), Falera (GR), Luzein (GR), Mustér (GR), Riom-Parsonz (GR), Salouf (GR), Sur (GR), Trimmis (GR), entre 1285 et 
<quantity box="[775,864,492,519]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.92" pageId="2" pageNumber="125" unit="m" value="1920.0">1920 m</quantity>
. Collectés entre 1994 et 2001 par J. &amp; R. Bärfuss.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1134,288,757]" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">
Cette espèce est difficilement distinguable des espèces 
<taxonomicName authority="(van der Goot, 1960)" baseAuthorityName="van der Goot" baseAuthorityYear="1960" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Dasysyrphus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="125" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="friuliensis">
<emphasis box="[801,954,560,586]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">D. friuliensis</emphasis>
(van der Goot, 1960)
</taxonomicName>
et 
<taxonomicName authority="(Zetterstedt, 1843)" baseAuthorityName="Zetterstedt" baseAuthorityYear="1843" box="[251,583,594,620]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Dasysyrphus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="125" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hilaris">
<emphasis box="[251,362,594,620]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">D. hilaris</emphasis>
(Zetterstedt, 1843)
</taxonomicName>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="Bartsch H. &amp; Binkiewicz E. &amp; Klintbjer A. &amp; Raden A. &amp; Nasibov E." box="[593,828,594,621]" pageId="2" pageNumber="125" refId="ref2830" refString="Bartsch H., Binkiewicz E., Klintbjer A., Raden A. &amp; Nasibov E. 2009. Tvavingar: Blomflugor: Syrphinae. Diptera: Syrphidae: Syrphinae. Uppsala: ArtDatabanken, Sveriges lantbruksuniversitet, 406 pp." type="book" year="2009">Bartsch et al. (2009)</bibRefCitation>
permettent de différencier ces espèces très semblables, mais leur identification reste délicate et nécessite une certaine expérience. Il n’est pas étonnant que 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Stys &amp; Moucha" baseAuthorityYear="1962" box="[682,863,662,688]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Dasysyrphus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="125" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="postclaviger">
<emphasis box="[682,863,662,688]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">D. postclaviger</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
ait souvent été confon- du avec 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="van der Goot" baseAuthorityYear="1960" box="[251,403,696,722]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Dasysyrphus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="125" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="friuliensis">
<emphasis box="[251,403,696,722]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">D. friuliensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
ni que cette espèce apparaisse également en 
<collectingCountry box="[933,1009,696,722]" name="Switzerland" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">Suisse</collectingCountry>
, étant déjà signalée des Alpes en 
<collectingCountry box="[407,488,731,757]" name="France" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">France</collectingCountry>
, au 
<collectingCountry box="[534,689,730,756]" name="Liechtenstein" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">Liechtenstein</collectingCountry>
et en 
<collectingCountry box="[758,859,730,756]" name="Austria" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">Autriche</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Speight M. C. D." box="[874,1029,730,757]" pageId="2" pageNumber="125" refId="ref3524" refString="Speight M. C. D. 2020. Species accounts of European Syrphidae (Diptera), Vol. 104. Syrph the Net Publications, Dublin, 314 pp." type="book" year="2020">Speight 2020</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
